column3:
“I don't know how I can give this one less than a 10. An outstanding recommendation from my local shop.

I use pot for autism regulation, and this one is just a gem, for me.

Makes the constant state of outrage just slide away, so you can get on with your day, and type up useful reviews for other autistic folks. :)”
“The Nightime, Sniffling, Sneezing, Coughing, Aching, Stuffyhead, Fever, So-You-Can-Rest Medicine.”
“It is actually sparkley! I may just be high as fuck though. Intense head/body high but then everything turned amazing. Lasted a decent time and smelled loud as fuck. Gotta luv Diamond OG”

“Back for more! Picked up some (Blood) Diamond OG as they call it,from Squishy Wishes. One joint between two people. A really heavy hitter. After a few minutes of hitting it, I got a headrush, and was on the couch stuck for about 30 minutes. Got the munchies after. The real deal. PM only!”

“Recreational attributes: It is a true Indica indeed. Its a great night time strain. Very relaxing and nice to enjoy a movie.

Medical Attributes: Great for pain relief and muscle spasms. It can also be useful for insomnia in higher dosage. Also a pretty decent appetite stimulant.

Effects: The high is surprisingly not too much of a couch lock"
column4: it starts off as a pretty euphoric

column3: “One of the best I've smoked besides Fire og.. Definitely one for the everyday smokers. Great High body and mind...”

“I am a huge fan of indicas that plaster you to the couch, but I do like that I can smoke this during the day and not be so stoned that I can't function. I can still do chores, exercise, and stay focused. Stay at home mom approved.”

“This strain should be rated waaaaaay higher than 7.9 that was probably the biggest disappointment with this strain: the leafly rating. it reads 7.9 right now but i rated this a 10/10 because i picked it up from a dispensary near my house. THC% = 28% and CBD= 1.8% it was fresh and healthy seriously one of the best strains i've had in my lifetime.”

“I'm an extremely picky and lightweight spoiled on my flower choices due to growing up on the hill. That being said I've seen this flower from 2-4 diff growers and has always been an A list strain . Super potent indica , I've seen tested at 28%( by far highest thc content seen from this strain) . It's a beautiful flower , incredibly dense and incredibly smooth flavor smoke. I have high high standards when it comes to ...”
“Nice strong Indica body high. One puff and you'll settle down.”

“An indica that I’ve been searching for!! My dispensary REALLY likes its Sativas & Hybribs but don’t carry many pure indica strains. So I usually just buy a hybrid. 

These buds are VERY pretty with a ton of purple & coated like sugar. It gives you that munchies, couch lock high thats great for insomnia & anxiety. It relaxes you but you can still have a conversation with someone & laugh your ass off. It does make you ...”

“Very nice knock out strain...good for evenings/bed time looks beautiful and smells potent but has a definite smell of BO! (bad odour) and even carries through in the taste a little...like OG Kush soaked in sweat :/ but it does the job qnd gets you to sleep”
“Don't smoke this and drive. I mean it.”

“Hard hitting Indica on the body. Perfect if you have muscle strains, cramps, anxiety, or are dealing with some form of stress in your life. very good for pain management.

Cloudy on Head (good for stress) 
Body Numbing (for Myofascial trigger points)”

“Being BI-POLAR 1 its a constant struggle between me and my brain. I treat people so they never want to talk to me again.Bi-Polar 1 destroys everything period.I came across DIAMOND OG here in Mesa AZ. I have to have this strain every day now.. When I get that MANIA rolling 1 rip off the bong and then the guilt pours in and the apologizes start. Not saying it removes bi-polar from you BUT it makes you realize when your...”

“Oh man this strains in my top 10 indica's.  Has  a citrus pine aroma, pretty trichromes.  The buzz slowly comes over me from head to toe melting the stress of the day away. If you need a reliable Indica go with this one.”

“Super chill stain. Out of all the indica's I've had, Dimond OG made the most sleepy. Which is what I want. The relaxing body high killed my depression and lower back pain. And left me feeling relaxed and sleepy.”

“Among the better kush varieties I've had the pleasure of coming across. The one complaint I've heard about it is that it's almost TOO strong! But really, its exactly what a top shelf kush strain should bring to the table. It's fragrant and floral, with a sour zing that makes you take notice. The stone is very deep and soothing, with moderate to heavy couchlock. As long as you don't have anything important to do, Diam...”
“Very relaxing strain, works great for muscle and joint pain.”
“Diamond OG will make you EXTREMELY tired. It's really good for insomnia and the flavour was pungent.”

“This is a great Indica strain. The one that I have is the Diamond OG in shatter concentrate form,  from Xtractology in California. Around 74% THC and around 4% terpenes. 

The description is dead on - this strain is a true indica. I've noticed after I take a nice dab, I'm very talkative at first and just have a relaxed, euphoric feeling throughout my body. Definitely an OG taste and smell, that comes out right up fro...”
“delicious. great OG smell. nice trichomes. heady and good body. good for getting you up to dance even if you hate to dance. social and happy high.”
“A really good Indica. Smoke a bowl and get happy, or smoke a joint and take a nap. =)”

“Very strong. Amazing body and head high. Gets me very chill and then sleepy afterwards. Definitely recommended before bed. I smoked this during the daytime and almost fell asleep in my patio chair trying to take a few more hits. Other than that, an awesome strain overall. would definitely 
be in the Top 5 of indica.”

“good strain, very heavy with a good head high. I definitely recommend it for insomnia. smells a little different than a pure OG. a bit more sweet and piney rather straight pinesol funk. Very light green and frosty”
“A really good Indica. Smoke a bowl and get happy, or smoke a joint and take a nap. =)”
“Oh my fucking god this strain rapes almost all other strains”

“Diamond OG provides me with great relief. This strain was exceptional helpful for my Crohn's Disease. This strain helped alleviate my PTSD, chronic nausea, intermittent and constant pain, as well as muscle spasms.  If you do not have much tolerance, this strain will probably make you tired after a bowl or 2, but if you have chronic symptoms that other strains barely touch(help elevate)...this one is probably for you”

“Got a great concentrate that works wonders with this one, if you are in pain or just totally depressed this Diamond OG Sugar Sap straight knocks you out, one of my top 5 concentrates easily and I recommend it to all! Got it from Magnolia Wellness. Definitely has not let me down one bit. If you see it try to try it or just get some, have to trust me on this people! So damn Dan! Hopefully my pics show up ✌.”
“This is my preferred high. Heavy in the eyes, tingly in the face, numb to the toes. Perfect.”

“So, I lit up a joint and started puffing off it and it was crazy, my high kicked in fast. Everything was happy and it felt like heaven. There was nothing bad in my mind. I would DEFINITELY recommend this for people with depression and stress.”

“Combining this with Sunshine #4 and Sour cookies will make you feel like you have phantom limb, even though it’s there. Not to be insensitive to those who actually have phantom limb and your limb isn’t actually there.”

“Combining this with Sunshine #4 and Sour cookies will make you feel like you have phantom limb, even though it’s there. Not to be insensitive to those who actually have phantom limb and your limb isn’t actually there.”

“Got a great concentrate that works wonders with this one, if you are in pain or just totally depressed this Diamond OG Sugar Sap straight knocks you out, one of my top 5 concentrates easily and I recommend it to all! Got it from Magnolia Wellness. Definitely has not let me down one bit. If you see it try to try it or just get some, have to trust me on this people! So damn Dan! Hopefully my pics show up ✌.”
“Dank 🔥”

“Diamond OG is one of my favorite strains! You feel the rush pretty instantaneously, and its a great rush! VERY relaxing, uplifting, excellent for pain, nausea, and increasing appetite! It also gave me some creative juices (as i like to draw a lot) and i think that if you have some social anxiety this strain will help! I dont have social anxiety, im actually pretty comfortable going up to strangers and what not, meeti...”

“One of the loudest of the OG's, the smell honestly sets the bar too damn high, cause after a joint i got this meh  thas it?! feeling followed by a sativa like uppity detail your car feeling, so i rolled another, smoked it 3/4 through  i went straight to the other side of chill unmotivated, pushing the buttons on the remote is too much work to ask of a man, this infomercials gonna do.  followed by a boring dont talk t...”
“Very tasty almost a deep cherry especially if in concentrate form. Thumbs up.”
“It was AMAZING!!!!!! Everytime I smoked this magnificent strain, I would get extremely euphoric and extremely tired.”

“Diamond OG is hands down one of the best Indica strains I've ever had. I wasn't expecting a head high along with the body high, and it does last for quite a while. Once some time passes this strain will knock you smooth out if you're not careful😜”
“Best Strain in the history of the planet”

“Just tried out this great strain. Hits after 2-3 puffs and creates a sudden happy type of vibe. No paranoia at all, you feel great and energized. Like always, the coming down part sucks. Overall good strand.”

“This is one of those strains that will never get old. 
I get a very Earthy/Sweet smell from these buds. 
Solid bud structure, almost reminds me of Bubba Kush.
It smokes like it taste, sweet on the inhale and a earthy, organic after taste. 
It's a very heavy mellow high, great for pain/anxiety/ and stress.”
“some of the best stuff i have ever smoked it is bomb”
“Very tasty almost a deep cherry especially if in concentrate form. Thumbs up.”

“This is definitely one of the best strains I've smoked in a while. The bud has such a beautiful appearance and texture accompanied by a delightfully fresh and sweet smell, which is also a nice way of describing its smooth flavour. You don't want the joint to end once you have a puff of this stuff and get lost in how much you are in enjoying it. Such a nice smooth stoned buzz, that hits pretty hard, but doesn't last t...”

“Love the smell of this one, extremely pungent with heavy pine and earthy terpenes. The buds aren't overly big but glisten like diamonds under light. Hits fast and hard felt first in the forehead, then a deep relaxing buzz quickly encompasses the rest of my body. Made me want to sit my ass down and chill, forget, relax, get the munchies and unwind from a long day. Perfect indica, top notch, love it. We recommend this ...”
“Smooth in a doob, tastes awesome, I love it.”

“Love the smell of this one, extremely pungent with heavy pine and earthy terpenes. The buds aren't overly big but glisten like diamonds under light. Hits fast and hard felt first in the forehead, then a deep relaxing buzz quickly encompasses the rest of my body. Made me want to sit my ass down and chill, forget, relax, get the munchies and unwind from a long day. Perfect indica, top notch, love it. We recommend this ...”
“Real heady high. Hits strong and mellows. Very relaxing and comfortable high.”

“Pleasant to look at, smell , and smoke. An indica through and through. painkiller, stress reducer, insomnia crusher in a higher dose. 
rich flavours. complex on the palate.”
“I have some 5 Star Diamond OG, almost the same just a few more good indica and kush strains crossed into it, super flame.”

“Used in oil form. This strain had me feeling a way I haven't felt on cannabis in a longggg time. I was able to stay totally alert and doing things while also being totally freakin baked. It was a spacey type high for sure... the more I smoked the more confidence I got. i highly recommend this for people that are having depression or motivation issues”

“This is definitely one of the best strains I've smoked in a while. The bud has such a beautiful appearance and texture accompanied by a delightfully fresh and sweet smell, which is also a nice way of describing its smooth flavour. You don't want the joint to end once you have a puff of this stuff and get lost in how much you are in enjoying it. Such a nice smooth stoned buzz, that hits pretty hard, but doesn't last t...”

“So the other day I picked up a strain called Diamond 💎 OG from Manny the Masterful. Two grams was a good sampling for the first time experiment. Had some pain this morning in my hip due to the cold and toked up on some Diamond 💎 OG flower 🌺. I can tell I am becoming medicated by the feeling of tingling in my face. I was comfortable and soon was delightfully lifted. Having a conversation with anyone while on this s...”

“This strain is literally the definition of an Indica. Immediately after smoking all my pain and stress had diminished and I was ready for bed. Can't tell you much about the high itself because I passed out about 15 minutes later. Definitely should be kept next to the NyQuil.”
“Super crystally, diamond og is a really pretty strain to look at, this one really is a gem. The telltale og genetics really come through in the smell, taste, and potency.”
“I have some 5 Star Diamond OG, almost the same just a few more good indica and kush strains crossed into it, super flame.”

“This is definitely one of the best strains I've smoked in a while. The bud has such a beautiful appearance and texture accompanied by a delightfully fresh and sweet smell, which is also a nice way of describing its smooth flavour. You don't want the joint to end once you have a puff of this stuff and get lost in how much you are in enjoying it. Such a nice smooth stoned buzz, that hits pretty hard, but doesn't last t...”

“Diamond OG is yet another OG Kush mash-up, this time with an unknown strain. The smell and taste is a slightly mediocre pine mixed with light hints of the OG Kush chemical-like terpene profile. The truly impressive aspect was the bud's appearance-under the magnifying glass and light it looked like it had been dipped in a billion tiny crystals. Although the high wasn't 100%, this is still a decent quality strain.”

“Very surprised by this strain. Bough on a sale thinking eh... some cheap leaf I can use till good stuff comes in. Well I was wrong love this stuff, so mellow and chill could vape all day long. The first wave of the  high is a big hit then levels in mins to a long lasting stone. Longer then I am used too. Hours after playing some games realized 4 hours breezed by. Dam..  High marks”

“The smell is absolutely phenomenal. That true OG funk..just DANK smell like weed should be. The taste is very similar to the smell. The smoke is pretty smooth considering this is extremely potent. Full indica stone in the eyelids and body. Serious couchlock. I love OG”

“This strain is literally the definition of an Indica. Immediately after smoking all my pain and stress had diminished and I was ready for bed. Can't tell you much about the high itself because I passed out about 15 minutes later. Definitely should be kept next to the NyQuil.”

“My dark 😈side took over and ignored the warnings lol. Wife and I smoked it early morning before starting our day & I ended up calling out from work. The relaxation off this strain can’t compare... yet lol. I couldn’t get out of bed🔒I couldn’t shake it off and my wife ended up feeling lazy and sleepy😴 
Great for pain and stress on my part. Remember don’t use as a wake n bake 😅”

p.s I make coconut oil infused with cannabis and this is really good just take 1 gram bud and de carb.

“my first time using anything other than unknown street sold pot.   using the concentrate form from dank vapes.   the first time, I overdid it.    i forgot how potent these are, and took way too many hits.   I've done street dabs,  so i thought i could handle it.    i was okay,  I just got very dizzy and nauseous.  now that I've got s better grasp on dosage, this is one amazing strain.  nice body buzz that I look for,...”
“I have a lot of anxiety and this strain is perfect. I get this super relaxing body and head feel but still very aware. Really love this strain!”
“Just picked up a few Gs of this strain after I got off work and it’s defiantly heady at first then knocks you out as you lay down to a deep quiet slumber it’s certainly a good night time strain”
“Perfect night time medicine.”
“This strain makes me feel FADED. Couch lock isn't too bad. I can still be active if I want to. Munchies will happen.”
“3 stars for an Indica is pretty good for me as they are generally not my style.”
“It’s one of the best strains I’ve ever smoked, from the citrusy taste to the high. It’s my favorite atm. It’s a great strain if u haven’t tried it you definitely should.”
“this is a fabulous medical. it gets rid of nausea and anxiety in a pinch, and got a nice, subtle taste. one of my favorites.”
“denifintly a nice body high. this is a really mellow flower”
“Had me stupid high 13 year smoker and this shit had me zombie mode after 10 hits off a cartridge. Stupid high use before bed only.”
“This strain is a great strain right before you go to bed it gives you the perfect relaxed sensation”
“great for after work relaxation!”
“Wonderful”

“Great strain, works awesome for pain wether it be chronic or acute. I medicate every night and this makes me comfortable enough to just drift off into la la land. I’ve used this during the day and am still able to remain motivated to get things done. I like this one I hope I get to medicate with it again soon.”
“My fingers are getting numb while typing this review. Anyway, a strong, wonderful, relaxation. Perfect for a lazy Saturday smoke. Very strong hit.”
“Upper with pain relief, take small hits”

“This strain provided a great deal of pain relief, it also made me extremely relaxed and also caused very little followup fatigue the day after smoking before bed, it's like if you removed all the negative parts of Rockstar Kush and Tuna Kush and increased the level of pain relief and relaxation at the expense of duration (4hr), this has been my favorite strain to date, I oonly received a small amount of it because wh...”

“Slept when I wanted to stay awake
Stayed awake when I wanted to sleep.”
“one of the most relaxing strains I've ever tried. definitely delivers a Netflix and Chill vibe.”

“I'm a heavy smoker and an indica and OG fan - saying that ; this strain is fantastic . I could write a ten page paper discussing the perks of this strain but to make it short 10/10- one of the best I've ever smoked”
“one of the most relaxing strains I've ever tried. definitely delivers a Netflix and Chill vibe.”
“Great strain and great shop overall!!! Will definitely be back”
“Delightful strain that packs a huge punch. Flavor to effect, Diamond is surely carrying its name proud as pristine and a find with showing off!”
“Nice buds, good fruity flavor, but the high wasnt to my liking, it was a mellow relaxation, but wasnt too strong. Good strain overall!”
“one of the most relaxing strains I've ever tried. definitely delivers a Netflix and Chill vibe.”

“Loved this strain. The medical effects were dead on. Some very good bud. When i got its the smallest nug of the bunch was 1.3 grams. Some flame if you love pure indicas and kush is you passion i reccomend this 1 of the flowers ive seen or smoked”
“Delightful strain that packs a huge punch. Flavor to effect, Diamond is surely carrying its name proud as pristine and a find with showing off!”
“Nice buds, good fruity flavor, but the high wasnt to my liking, it was a mellow relaxation, but wasnt too strong. Good strain overall!”
“Diamond OG had a nice clear sharp taste that made my mouth water, i found that when my throat was dry it had a unique taste but it still covered this with a nice high”
“Very uplifting high, doesn't make you a couch potato all day I would say. This high keeps me focused, happy, and energetic. I think I'm in love with the body high.”
“Had a great first time experience will def. Be calling again”
“A knock out! One of the few strains that will put me on the couch. Smoked a joint between my wife and I and it had me stuck. One of the hardest hitting indica strains I've ever hit.”
“Delightful strain that packs a huge punch. Flavor to effect, Diamond is surely carrying its name proud as pristine and a find with showing off!”

“this is a good strain f/ pain,relaxing and just winding down in general.rolled a joint and smoked it.it comes on pretty quick and lasts about an hour or so on me.earthy,spicy tasting.it`s a good one and will buy again.”
“it's wonderful for pain and helps me pass right out its super dense and frosty”
“Good, long lasting, giggly, creative. helps with insomnia.”
“Nice buds, good fruity flavor, but the high wasnt to my liking, it was a mellow relaxation, but wasnt too strong. Good strain overall!”
“Fantasterific!”
“Had a great first time experience will def. Be calling again”

“Very good strain makes you feel so happy and relaxed”
“A knock out! One of the few strains that will put me on the couch. Smoked a joint between my wife and I and it had me stuck. One of the hardest hitting indica strains I've ever hit.”
“Definitely helped with stress. I didn’t get dry mouth though. But then again I don’t open my mouth often.”
“bout a preroll blunt of this strain and wasnt upset with my pick blunt was real fat and burned slow definatly tasted the hierba in it the colas were powder coated in crystals almost”
“Great tasting, great smelling, and great long effects. 4 out of 5 stars for Outstanding!!”
“very good strain for pain I recently had some extensive dental work done and so far as been able to help keep the pains away for night time relief.”
“Very potent; appearance automatically intrigues the user due to its unusually high crystal content. Small - Medium density of buds that bust up nicely, good strain for a relaxing night. 3.5/5”
“A must-buy for sure. 10/10”

“Normally, with Indica strains I lose complete track of time and even get events in a slightly wrong order. Of course, I do that when I don't use, just not as much. But with Diamond OG, I was able to be lucid though very sedated. 

I could actually follow the action adventure film I was watching and even had the peace of mind to give it 3/5 stars. Normally, I just say they're all 5's when I vape a strong strain like t...”
“Mostly chill and happy body high”

“Very relaxing strain. I had a great deal of tension in my lower back prior to smoking that was taken care of almost completely. Anxiety levels, which are typically always on the high/manic end, lowered noticeably as well. A new favorite.”
“In a blunt pretty good”
“Stick colas”

“The name kind of sets up an impression for my that this strain is like top quality and mainstream and honestly the flavor is really smooth, it has a slight skunk taste but mainly tastes piney and a little citrus. Hits really smooth and for some reason there is a really small sativa high in my opinion, that is a little psychedelic and keeps you awake but the moment you rip it the mood changes immediately and all anxie...”

“This strain was absolutely A2. After a painful gym session , I planned to take a .5 dose .After inhaling the dosage, I instantly felt the relaxation go all through out my body, giving a eutrophic feeling.”

“This is by far one of the best Indica strains I've ever smoked. Light and fluffy. Hypnotizing aroma. The high had me on couch lock and lasted a couple hours. Made my eye lids feel super heavy. I'd get again.”
“Very good . When smoking , it hits the chest . Comes off a bit strong , but worth it at the end .”

“Have to say not my favourite buzz but it's lack of knowledge prior to smoking it. Was out golfing and took a few hits which left me a little confused and my game even worse. I could imagine enjoying this solo in front of a movie; may give it a try again.”

“Pretty good. Smells very lemony. Not a great every day smoke as your tolerance will build up to it quickly. Great for all types of pain and headaches and such. Doesn't have much anti-depressant qualities unless used in a large dose. Definitely the right choice after a long  and busy day.”

“My friend brought this over as a backup in case we ran out of our usual, but I would not recommend it. Yes, everything was absolutely hilarious, however, it came with a price. I felt really uncomfortable and had an intense body high, tripping over all sorts of shit. I would not recommend it to someone looking to relieve stress or feel happy, this is a strain that fucks you up big time. If that's your game, by all mea...”
“Great bud, awesome taste, looks beautiful.”
“Perfect strain... Good nights sleep, relaxing, full body high. Great for strained muscles and stress relief. Definitely one of my favs...!”

“let me start off by saying I've been looking all over for this and i finally found it very earthy tasted nice almost hashy aroma very pungent but not skunky had me stoned to the bone you have definitely got to try this”
“Esta llerba esta chidisima compa”
“A heady buzz that also gave my arms a 'heavy' sensation.  Made my mouth dry, good for a during the day med.”
“amazing full body smooth euphoria. Good before bed for a nice and smooth slip into slumber. heavy on the eyes, not recommended if you want to be productive or have to work. my favorite so far”
“Excellent strain right here. Has put me on my ass more than a couple of times. Very dank and if you don't smoke too much it won't have you too couchlocked.”

“I've read many good reviews on this strain so I decided to give it a try. So far it has changed the way I evaluate my strains. Immediate effect, but with such a smooth feeling. Melts away the days stress with such a relaxed effect. My new go to sleep or just relax strain. I'm a fan!”
“very very very good strain!!! A little more of a cough than i like but it is one of my new favorites.”
“Tingly fo sho”

“heavy indica noticeable right out the gate, the bud smells amazing, but leaves me wanting more outta it. good somewhat balanced high, blood red eyes, and after 2 nice bowls i was out like a light. good high to end the day, not for your active stoner”
“Complex flavor profile for a potent indica. Frosty nugs! Great before night time.”
“Amazing strain, i signed up just to rate it!”
